sh and \\cf1 each of the designated citywide languages as defined in section 23-1101 of the administrative code.\\cf0\\par\n\\ulnone\\'a7 2. This local law takes effect 90 days after it becomes law. \\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\qj\\fs18\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\nNJC/ACK\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar LS 6957\\par\n11/1/202111:23 pm\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n}\n",
